Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.83,0:00:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}The dreams embraced by a single life{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.84,0:00:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}are boundless beyond even the stars.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.84,0:00:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}The dreams that we foster over time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.85,0:00:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}are waiting for the moment{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}when we come upon them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.53,0:00:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}The words we exchange{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}make our hearts tremble,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.53,0:00:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}and a chance meeting{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}could change the future.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.21,0:01:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}People, no matter who they are,{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}as they pursue their dreams,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.48,0:01:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}have the courage to travel new paths.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.15,0:01:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}As we leave behind a living{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}testament of our journey,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.49,0:01:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}the Galaxy Railways on which{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}we travel continue ever on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.85,0:01:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}An unknown threat is{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}attacking the Galaxy Railways.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.85,0:01:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}And now, in order to save all fate,{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}which is about to be crushed,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.19,0:01:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}and to once again{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}carve out a new tomorrow,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.53,0:01:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Big One,{\i0} move out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.20,0:01:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Young people depart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.88,0:02:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}"Echoes of Life"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.82,0:02:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Father, that train is the only one\N{\c&He1e1e1&}going the other way. Where is it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.16,0:02:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That is an SDF combat train.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.16,0:02:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}SDF? The Space Defense Force?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.83,0:02:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That's train number 001, {\i1}Big One.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.18,0:02:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That is the hope of the Galaxy Railways.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Big One!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:03:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The fate that is about to be lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The only things that can take it back\N{\c&He1e1e1&}are the spirits of resolute men,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.17,0:03:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}and a fervent desire to fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.14,0:03:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.92,0:03:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.92,0:03:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Defense Fortress Annex.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.26,0:03:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Headquarters has stationed it near Destiny\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to defend against external enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.93,0:03:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It's one of our\N{\c&He1e1e1&}unmanned military stations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.60,0:03:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Normally, it is used\N{\c&He1e1e1&}as a backup switchyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}While this fortress is drawing\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the attention of the Alfort fleet,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.27,0:03:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Big One{\i0} will finish\N{\c&He1e1e1&}refurbishing its main guns,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}and make a short warp to right above them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.28,0:03:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}As we move down toward the fleet,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}we'll launch our attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.62,0:04:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Our target is the Alfort flagship,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}this large battleship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Paralyze their command systems\N{\c&He1e1e1&}and then wipe them out all at once, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This is our last stronghold;\N{\c&He1e1e1&}if they break through, our fate is sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We have to protect the Galaxy Railways,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.00,0:04:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}And then make sure we come back safely!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Got that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}- Roger!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}- Roger!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}- Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.26,0:04:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Y- Yuuki-kun...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Louis!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}I can still feel your warmth...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.88,0:05:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Louis... I promise you, I will defend{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}the Galaxy Railways with my life,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.88,0:05:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}which you saved.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.56,0:05:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuuki, I'm entrusting all of\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the weapons systems to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.23,0:05:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You're taking over for Bruce.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Do him proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.23,0:05:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.90,0:05:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Manabu, I'm counting on you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.91,0:05:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.58,0:05:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The squad that was assigned to inspect\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the battlefield and rescue our comrades
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.32,0:05:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}recovered you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}As a specimen, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.25,0:05:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}There was something I wanted to ask you,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}so you're temporarily in my custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.93,0:05:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Why did you have this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}She...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.87,0:06:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Leafle-san...{\i0} passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.88,0:06:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The Alfort fleet will\N{\c&He1e1e1&}reach Annex in 2200 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.55,0:06:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Starting up all of\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Annex's defense systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.89,0:06:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Remote control intercept is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.90,0:06:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What is {\i1}Big One's{\i0} position and status?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.23,0:06:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}They are 15,000 spacekilos from Destiny.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}New main gun systems are 95% complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.24,0:06:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}There isn't enough time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.91,0:06:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Unfortunately, the damage to the engine\N{\c&He1e1e1&}was worse than we thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}and the particle cannons and\N{\c&He1e1e1&}pressure valves were hit pretty badly,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.35,0:06:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}and won't be of any use.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.92,0:06:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I see. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It just has to get us as far as Annex.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It may have taken a royal beating,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}but {\i1}Iron Berger{\i0} isn't dead yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:07:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}If the particle cannons won't work,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}couple us up to some Gustav guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.53,0:07:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Two cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.87,0:07:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Y- you can't mean... That's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hey, we'll have {\i1}Big One{\i0} tow us back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.54,0:07:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.54,0:07:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}And if we get hurt,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}there's always {\i1}Yuki-chan,{\i0} right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.55,0:07:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}All right, now that that's settled,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}let's get something to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.55,0:07:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}- Roger!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}- Roger!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}- Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.55,0:07:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}J- just a minute, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.89,0:07:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The Alfort fleet has\N{\c&He1e1e1&}entered Annex's firing range.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.23,0:07:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Draw them in as much as you can.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Don't fire the first shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We have to buy whatever time\N{\c&He1e1e1&}we can for {\i1}Big One.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.90,0:07:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Commander! All ships in the\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Alfort fleet are reducing speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.57,0:07:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.92,0:07:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The Alfort fleet has come to a halt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.59,0:07:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Leafle, how foolish of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.53,0:08:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}My younger sister was\N{\c&He1e1e1&}an outstanding scientist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}But she was too idealistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.20,0:08:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The Cosmo Matrix has been handed over\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to the Galaxy Railways, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.21,0:08:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm letting you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.21,0:08:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Go back to Yuuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.22,0:08:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}H- how do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.55,0:08:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You called out his name many times.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}He must be someone dear to you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.23,0:08:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Receiving a message\N{\c&He1e1e1&}from the Alfort fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.90,0:08:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}"To Galaxy Railways Headquarters:\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Surrender your home station at once."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This works to our advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.41,0:08:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Respond to them\N{\c&He1e1e1&}that we are considering it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}and to give us some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.91,0:09:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Big One, in the meantime,{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}get those new main guns completed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The calm before the storm, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Stick Annex right into the middle\N{\c&He1e1e1&}of that fleet. Aim for the flagship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.54,0:09:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I- I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That will put an end\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to this once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Ride this out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You pilot it with your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.24,0:09:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}My name is Treele.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.27,0:09:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm grateful to you for looking\N{\c&He1e1e1&}after my sister when she passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.91,0:09:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm Louis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:10:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I won't forget it. Now, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.58,0:10:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.25,0:10:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Why have you started this fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.25,0:10:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Leafle didn't want us to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.16,0:10:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That's why she risked her life\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to deliver the Cosmo Matrix to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I know! But there's no\N{\c&He1e1e1&}going back for us now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.60,0:10:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}...if we want to stay alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}you can come with me, can't you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.84,0:10:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Together, we can prevent\N{\c&He1e1e1&}any more casualties!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Let's put a stop to this fight, Treele!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.61,0:10:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Go, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Treele!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.62,0:10:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Where is the prisoner?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}She's not here. Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Get out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.62,0:10:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Ivanov, what are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'll turn you into space dust!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.58,0:11:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Take this man away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Annex is advancing on the fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.26,0:11:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What's going on!? That wasn't the plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.61,0:11:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.91,0:12:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The Cosmo Matrix?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.91,0:12:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yes, that's the thing that\N{\c&He1e1e1&}my sister made off with.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.58,0:12:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I do recall hearing about a combat train
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.35,0:12:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}that shot down one of\N{\c&He1e1e1&}our ships with one shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.92,0:12:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Ever since then, there have been no\N{\c&He1e1e1&}such reports from any of our task forces
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.19,0:12:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}that have defeated the Galaxy Railways.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.26,0:12:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}However, Foresis-sama,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}if it has been analyzed...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We are already approaching\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the heart of the Galaxy Railways.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.27,0:12:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Those who are putting up a last\N{\c&He1e1e1&}struggle will not last a single moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We must carry out the orders\N{\c&He1e1e1&}of our Master, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We will resume our attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.95,0:12:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Annex has been destroyed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.95,0:12:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Damn it! What is\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Headquarters trying to do!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bulge, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.89,0:13:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Commander...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.56,0:13:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Was it that Ivanov bastard!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.23,0:13:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What is the current status of the fleet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}They were not damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}They have resumed their advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.24,0:13:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Range: 8000 spacekilos!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.91,0:13:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Julia, don't you die!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.25,0:13:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}When I get back, let me hear your\N{\c&He1e1e1&}answer to what we talked about earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.94,0:13:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We've gotten the output from\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the main engine back up to 70%,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.94,0:13:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}but with the Gustav guns coupled in,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}your mobility will be lowered even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.28,0:13:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.95,0:14:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.89,0:14:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}May you be victorious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.56,0:14:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Iron Berger{\i0} has moved\N{\c&He1e1e1&}into launch position!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.89,0:14:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.56,0:14:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Murase!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.89,0:14:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Please relax! We'll protect\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Big One{\i0}, you just watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.57,0:14:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We're counting on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.91,0:14:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Iron Berger,{\i0} move out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.25,0:14:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Multiple thermal bodies approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.92,0:14:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Track shields to full power!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.93,0:14:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Akatsuki-san,{\i0} what is the\N{\c&He1e1e1&}current status of your work?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.26,0:14:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What's going on? Has it started already?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.60,0:14:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}A track ring has been destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.60,0:14:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Damn it! The second unit\N{\c&He1e1e1&}has been wrecked!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We don't have any spares!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.60,0:14:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}If that won't work,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}then slap in a bypass!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.27,0:14:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.94,0:14:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Old-timer...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.28,0:14:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}...lend me your strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.88,0:15:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Prepare to intercept!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.22,0:15:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Strafing fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.89,0:15:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Multiple large-scale thermal bodies\N{\c&He1e1e1&}identified within the Alfort fleet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Are they planning to finish us off!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.90,0:15:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Akatsuki-san!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You've got to wait a little longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Iron Berger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.58,0:15:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Vega Platoon!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yo! Came to lend you a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Murase!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.59,0:15:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Iron Berger,{\i0} head open!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.26,0:15:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}All right, what do you say\N{\c&He1e1e1&}we give 'em hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}They did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.22,0:16:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain Murase!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.55,0:16:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Murase, we thank you for the support.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.89,0:16:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Don't worry about it!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}This is the usual routine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.23,0:16:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}There's more of them left\N{\c&He1e1e1&}than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hurry and recharge the Gustavs!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.23,0:16:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Reading a large discharge\N{\c&He1e1e1&}from the enemy fleet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.57,0:16:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Murase!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Schneider!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.25,0:16:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hurry! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.59,0:16:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That could be... a little difficult...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You're not!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.59,0:16:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Stay there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:16:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Take care of things from here on...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.53,0:17:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Schneider!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Schneider!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.21,0:17:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Those bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.23,0:17:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Jose!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.23,0:17:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Jose! Jose!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.90,0:17:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That... was a nice... bath...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.91,0:17:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Jose...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Murase!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Not to worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This will just be... one more scar...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.25,0:17:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Akatsuki-san!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Just a little longer! Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.92,0:17:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bypass connection complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}All right! We're almost done!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.86,0:18:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Murase, that's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.53,0:18:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Get out of there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.53,0:18:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Reading discharges from the enemy fleet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.20,0:18:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The largest ones yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.54,0:18:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Don't you mess with the toughest dudes...\N{\c&He1e1e1&}in the universe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.21,0:18:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.90,0:18:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Big One... the Galaxy Railways...{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}and our future... is in your hands.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.52,0:19:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Julia... forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.20,0:19:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The work is completed!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Blow 'em away, Manabu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.21,0:19:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What's the matter, Manabu!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.88,0:19:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.21,0:19:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu! Get it together, Manabu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.22,0:19:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Prepare to fire the main guns!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.22,0:19:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Target: The Alfort fleet flagship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.89,0:19:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Fire!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.24,0:19:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}All shots on target!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.24,0:19:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.91,0:19:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Full speed ahead! We're plowing\N{\c&He1e1e1&}into the heart of the enemy fleet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.93,0:20:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Jose...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.60,0:20:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Silver...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.27,0:20:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Schneider...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.60,0:20:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Captain Murase...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.58,0:21:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Murase...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.08,0:21:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Lives... are echoing...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Their dreams... will be carried on...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.28,0:21:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}How many nights have{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}I spent alone since then?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.29,0:22:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Constantly having dreams of the hope{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}that you are, as I lightly sleep.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.97,0:22:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}The smiles and tears that{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}you gave to me and me alone{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.98,0:22:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}come to mind every time{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}I get disheartened,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.32,0:22:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}and I set forth again toward the morrow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.99,0:22:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}The joyful light of the galaxy beckons me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.60,0:22:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}to that beloved person within my heart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.61,0:22:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}No matter how far apart we are,{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}my memories will never fade.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.28,0:23:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}My heart wishes always{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}to be at your side.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.30,0:23:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}The railways carry our hopes and dreams.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.31,0:23:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}It doesn't matter that we don't{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}know where they are going.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.31,0:23:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Fate is something that we{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}make for ourselves, after all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.98,0:23:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Next time on Tales of the Galaxy Railways,{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Final Episode:{\i0} "Far-Reaching Hope"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.65,0:23:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}We're going to encounter{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}something at the next station.{\i0}